            <font size="3" face="Times New Roman, Times, serif"><strong>LABOR 
            ATTORNEY</strong>--Parmenter O'Toole is seeking candidates for an 
            Associate position as a labor attorney in representing a variety of 
            public and private sector employers. Candidates should have one to 
            three years' experience. This is an opportunity for challenging legal 
            work in a friendly work setting. Interested candidates are asked to 
            submit a resume, in confidence to: John C. Schrier, Parmenter O'Toole, 
            175 W. Apple Avenue, P.O. Box 786, Muskegon, MI 49443-0786 and visit 
            our website at <a href="http://www.parmenterlaw.com/"><b>http://www.parmenterlaw.com</b></a> 
            </font> 
            <p><a href="#classified"><b><font size=-2>Back to Quicklinks</font></b></a> 
              <br>
            <hr>
            <font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"><strong>LITIGATION 
            ATTORNEY--Delphi Automotive Systems</strong> is seeking an attorney 
            to manage intellectual property litigation. The successful applicant 
            will be admitted to practice in Michigan, have 5-12 years' experience 
            concentrating in intellectual property litigation, and have excellent 
            academic credentials including a science or engineering degree. Writing 
            skills will be tested. Admission to US PTO is desirable but not essential. 
            Send resume in confidence to Carolyn Fodor, 5725 Delphi Drive, M.C. 
            483-400-603, Troy, MI 48098-2815.</font> 
            <p><a href="#classified"><b><font size=-2>Back to Quicklinks</font></b></a> 
              <br>
            <hr>
            <b>MAJOR DETROIT LAW FIRM</b> seeks attorneys. We are looking for 
            attorneys with 0 to 2 years experience in Medical Malpractice law. 
            Candidate must have high academic credentials and have strong research 
            and writing skills. Submit resume and writing samples to P.O. Box 
            43158 Detroit, MI 48243. eoe 
            <p><a href="#classified"><b><font size=-2>Back to Quicklinks</font></b></a> 
            </p>
