            to three years' experience. This is an opportunity for challenging 
            legal work in a friendly work setting. Interested candidates are asked 
            to submit a resume, in confidence to: John C. Schrier, Parmenter O'Toole, 
            175 W. Apple Avenue, P.O. Box 786, Muskegon, MI 49443-0786 and visit 
            our website at <a href="http://www.parmenterlaw.com/"><b>http://www.parmenterlaw.com</b></a><br>
