            <b>MUNICIPAL ATTORNEYS WANTED</b>--Secrest, Wardle, Lynch seeks municipal 
            attorneys with at least 3 years experience to handle wide ranging 
            municipal work in its Farmington Hills office. Applicant must have 
            prior experience and possess strong academic, writing and advocacy 
            skills. Firm offers excellent salary and benefit package. E-mail resume 
            to Tom Azoni, tazoni@secrestwardle.com 
            <p><a href="#classified"><b><font size=-2>Back to Quicklinks</font></b></a> 
