            complex, commercial matters, including several class action lawsuits 
            as plaintiffs’ counsel. This position requires strong analytical skills. 
            The candidate’s duties will focus on all facets of litigation support, 
            including trial preparation. Candidates should work well independently 
            and be able to work efficiently in a dynamic environment. A resume 
            should be addressed to: Recruiting Coordinator, Wasinger Kickham and 
